{"tid":1799193,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"［值得一睇］北京限狗令","createTime":"2019-12-26T18:36:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T12:45:02.000Z","uid":144125,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6c0e3089c484bec90fceb365ddb19e7feb64cadd","tid":1799193,"uid":144125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T18:36:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/mOrhPVob_r4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FmOrhPVob_r4&d=TEMpI0ru4fZij%2BnpPgfFHRckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=27395c71\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mOrhPVob_r4</a><br />\n<br />\n帶返頭盔先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />條片係講普通話  亦都無字幕<br />\n拍片既係一位移居海外既華人<br />\n<br />\n片入面有介紹到「限狗令」既由來、影響等等<br />\n甚至借「限狗令」一事指出支那國既法制問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然呢D事情暫時與我地無關....<br />\n但假如香港有一日真係被中共全面統治  到時呢D事就會發生係各位貓奴狗奴身上<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以真係不容忽視<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">養寵物都關政治事！！！<br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n為左香港  為左未來   為左我地各位主子<br />\n各位要一齊抗共  一齊光復我地既香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f51df831ed148e86a62fb6b2207163ac4dadeab","tid":1799193,"uid":38539,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T19:03:43.000Z","msg":"但係呢度好多狗肉撚支持跟祖國法津恢復香港食狗權利..."},{"pid":"bccbaacf3e1e9f5926d797d9e4f886101c1fb279","tid":1799193,"uid":59684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T04:14:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed1d257ff43ec0aa9d0bd84bac56a855f6bc0640","tid":1799193,"uid":299372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f51